DOC.detailed_description: This three-part study . Part 1 : Part 1 study single dose , open-label , randomize crossover study healthy male female subject compare relative bioavailability two formulation FDL169 . Part 2 : Part 2 study multiple , escalate dose study three different dos test formulation FDL169 healthy male female subject evaluate PK profile test formulation FDL169 . Part 3 : Part 3 study single dose , open-label study male female subject CF determine PK profile test formulation FDL169 .
